{
  "id": "adv_event_2404_01_05_01",
  "title": "ジャック\nポット！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『今日はなんと日本から",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Tonight‚ we have very special guests—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.5666666666999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "トップアイドルが来てるんだ！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Top idols‚ all the way from Japan!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.5666666667,
      "endTime": 6.266666666700001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4099.999968100001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.4166666348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "おお。やっば、満員じゃん\nkanaが宣伝したお陰なんだから、感謝してよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Woah. Look‚ it’s packed.\nBe grateful‚ this is all thanks to my promotions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4666666348,
      "endTime": 15.3406350453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.5317688624
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "大して大きなステージではないけれど……\n日本のステージとは随分雰囲気が違うわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not that big of a stage…\nbut the atmosphere is quite different from stages in Japan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5317688624,
      "endTime": 22.2585605302,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "どこであっても\n満員の観客席をステージから見るのは最高ね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter where we are‚\nIt’s the best feeling to see a packed audience from the stage!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4496943473,
      "endTime": 27.1960210799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.3871548969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "最初は、「ラスベガスは日本とはレベルが違うから\n無名でもしゃーない」とか言ってたくせにさぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were saying‚ “Las Vegas is on a different level than Japan‚\nso it’s only natural that we’re unknown” though~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3871548969,
      "endTime": 34.3950234729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.58615729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "うっさいわね！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shut up!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.58615729,
      "endTime": 35.9677446046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.1588784216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "喧嘩は本番の後にしてちょうだい\n……そろそろ呼ばれるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Save your bickering for after the performance.\n…We’ll be called out soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1588784216,
      "endTime": 41.119753265199996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.3108870822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "よっしゃ\nそれじゃ――ⅢX、行くよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright.\nThen―― IIIX‚ let’s go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3108870822,
      "endTime": 47.0712499934,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7218.1661924000055
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12955.7795845
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2790532746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "『最強アイドル、『ⅢX』ーーーー！！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"The strongest idols‚ ‘IIIX’ーーーー!!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3290532746,
      "endTime": 57.391139666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.5957199412
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "『ラスベガスのみなさん、こんにちは！\n私達は日本から来た最強アイドルⅢXです！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Hello‚ everyone in Las Vegas!\nWe are IIIX‚ the strongest idols from Japan!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5957199412,
      "endTime": 65.6927041369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.883837954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "『今日は、たーっぷりkana達の魅力を見せつけて\nみんなを虜にしちゃうから！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Today‚ we’re going to show you all of kana's charms\nand captivate everyone!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.883837954,
      "endTime": 71.4024549164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.5935887334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2404_01_05-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "『変幻自在のステージから\n一瞬たりとも、目を離さないで下さいね――』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"With our ever-changing stage‚\ndon't take your eyes off us for even a second――\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.5935887334,
      "endTime": 76.5110680577,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}